# Meta (Facebook) Pixel ID from Meta Events Manager. Enables storefront-side ad
# tracking (PageView/ViewContent/AddToCart/InitiateCheckout) so Facebook ads can
# optimize + retarget. Same pixel the FB & Instagram channel uses for checkout.
# Leave blank to disable (the storefront pixel no-ops when empty).
PUBLIC_FACEBOOK_PIXEL_ID=""
